类 User

java.lang.Object
dao.mappers.User
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable
@Alias("User") public class User extends Object implements Serializable
User entity class representing a user in the recipe management system. This class is mapped to the database user table and contains user authentication information.
从以下版本开始:
1.0
